author: Taegan Goddard
title: Politics Moves Away from the Bushes
text:
Politics Moves Away from the Bushes October 24, 2015 By Taegan Goddard 0 Comments 
The New York Times reports that “those who have long been in the Bush family orbit are also being forced to reckon with a party that seems to be moving on from them.” 
Said former Gov. John Sununu (R), a longtime Bush family confidant: “I have no feeling for the electorate anymore. It is not responding the way it used to.
